# Flux HelmRelease API Version

Always use `helm.toolkit.fluxcd.io/v2` for HelmRelease resources. The `v2beta1` and `v2beta2` versions have been removed from the cluster.

```yaml
# ✅ GOOD
apiVersion: helm.toolkit.fluxcd.io/v2
kind: HelmRelease

# ❌ BAD — deprecated and removed
apiVersion: helm.toolkit.fluxcd.io/v2beta1
kind: HelmRelease
```
